lemand" lang="nds" hreflang="nds" class="interlanguage-link-target">Plattdüütsch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl"><a href="https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" title="Gérard Mourou — néerlandais" lang="nl" hreflang="nl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Nederlands</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no"><a href="https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" title="Gérard Mourou — norvégien bokmål" lang="nb" hreflang="nb" class="interlanguage-link-target">Norsk bokmål</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pl"><a href="https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" title="Gérard Mourou — polonais" lang="pl" hreflang="pl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Polski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pt"><a href="https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" title="Gérard Mourou — portugais" lang="pt" hreflang="pt" class="interlanguage-link-target">Português</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ro"><a href="https://ro.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" title="Gérard Mourou — roumain" lang="ro" hreflang="ro" class="interlanguage-link-target">Română</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ru"><a href="https://ru.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%9C%D1%83%D1%80%D1%83,_%D0%96%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%80" title="Муру, Жерар — russe" lang="ru" hreflang="ru" class="interlanguage-link-target">Русский</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-simple"><a href="https://simple.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" title="Gérard Mourou — Simple English" lang="en-simple" hreflang="en-simple" class="interlanguage-link-target">Simple English</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sr"><a href="https://sr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%96%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B0%D1%80_%D0%9C%D1%83%D1%80%D1%83" title="Жерар Муру — serbe" lang="sr" hreflang="sr" class="interlanguage-link-target">Српски / srpski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-sv"><a href="https://sv.wikipedia.org/wiki/G%C3%A9rard_Mourou" ti